<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.231433>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1 A – D. Brachypoda milicaae sp. n., male: A = dorsal shield; B = idiosoma, ventral view; C = palp; D = chelicera. Scale bars = 100 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/231433/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.231434>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2 A – B. Brachypoda milicaae sp. n., male: A = IV-L; B = IV-L- 4 – 6. Scale bar = 100 µm." ;
